data.description: Fully renovated in 2018 classic 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bath colonial home on a quiet street. Enter this home through a charming open-air front porch. This home has all newer windows, a French door leading to a huge deck and backyard. Beautiful updated kitchen with breakfast and open concept to the dining room, Quartz countertops stainless steel appliances. Newer custom tile bathroom, and beautiful hardwood floors throughout this home. Ample space for playroom in basement and attic. Four car driveway and free standing garage. This home is fully ADT security system.
